    "spell": {
        "name": "Heinous Future",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You hold up a fractured mirror to the target, and in that mirror it sees a thing that may yet come to pass\u2014a ghastly fortelling that the target instinctively knows is eerily possible. It's not a guaranteed thing, just a dreadful possibility, but it haunts the targets's thoughts all the same.",
